[TimeCloak](https://www.mhztimecloak.com/) is built for professionals who believe output matters more than activity percentages. With intelligent features including TimeBooster, Screen Tab Shifting, Automated Cursor Movement, Random Scrolling, and staying invisible on taskbar and task manager, TimeCloak helps create a smoother and less stressful remote work experience. Whether you work through Upwork, collaborate with international clients, or use workplace monitoring platforms like Hubstaff, Time Doctor, Clockify, Timely, or Apploye, TimeCloak is designed for remote developers, freelancers, and distributed teams who want to focus on delivering high quality work instead of constantly worrying about activity scores and excessive monitoring.
